  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个紧凑模式的甘特图，展示今天数据库清理任务和用户会话的时间分布。整体标题就叫\"GANTT compact\"，时间轴用小时和分钟显示，精确到秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "displayMode: compact",
        "title",
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，紧凑模式、标题已设置。时间格式我理解为HH:mm:ss，轴标签显示成\"12h30\"这种%Hh%M格式对吗？另外任务分几个区块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat HH:mm:ss",
        "axisFormat %Hh%M"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，时间格式确认。任务分两大区块：第一个是\"DB Clean\"，有7次清理，从12点开始每半小时一次；第二个是\"Sessions\"，有9个用户会话A到I，时间有重叠。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section DB Clean",
        "section Sessions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出两个section框架。DB Clean下7个Clean任务，时间分别是12:00、12:30、13:00、13:30、14:00、14:30、15:00开始，持续10m、12m、8m、9m、13m、10m、11m。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Clean: 12:00:00, 10m",
        "Clean: 12:30:00, 12m",
        "Clean: 13:00:00, 8m",
        "Clean: 13:30:00, 9m",
        "Clean: 14:00:00, 13m",
        "Clean: 14:30:00, 10m",
        "Clean: 15:00:00, 11m"
